release.name: RELEASE VERSION
release.body:
## What's Changed

* Add code to download mnist by @chaseWillden in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/4
* Implement tensor random and zeros functions. Add size to shape by @chaseWillden in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/5
* Fit model by @chaseWillden in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/6
* Adding new dataset CIFAR-10 and example project by @mjovanc in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/24
* Mnist Example with Adam Optimizer by @chaseWillden in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/25
* Add cross entropy loss by @chaseWillden in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/27
* Split out layers models by @mjovanc in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/33
* Loss decrease by @chaseWillden in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/39
* Adding optimization for performance and cleanup by @mjovanc in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/40
* Improving sequential model output while training by @mjovanc in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/43
* Save model by @chaseWillden in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/46
* Adding logging library by @chaseWillden in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/50
* Add imagenet_v2 by @chaseWillden in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/51
* Helper function adam by @mjovanc in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/52
* Adding println to fit function by @mjovanc in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/53
* Fix unit test, test_adam_optimizer_incompatible_shapes in adam.rs by @mjovanc in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/68
* Refactoring and cleanup by @mjovanc in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/70
* Impl validate func sequential model by @mjovanc in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/73
* Fix split_at to allow dynamic shapes by @chaseWillden in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/75
* Implement Xavier or He initialization of random weights by @chaseWillden in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/77
* Implement leaky relu by @chaseWillden in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/83
* Implements prelu by @chaseWillden in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/85
* Implement gelu by @chaseWillden in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/87
* Implement ada delta optimizer by @chaseWillden in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/92
* Implement the other optimizers by @chaseWillden in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/94
* Implements huber and mean aboslute error by @chaseWillden in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/96

## New Contributors
* @chaseWillden made their first contribution in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/4
* @mjovanc made their first contribution in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/24
* @dependabot made their first contribution in https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/pull/65

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/delta-rs/delta/commits/v0.1.0
